com.kairosive.utils

Class KSTimeUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kairosive.utils.KSTimeUtils

  • public class KSTimeUtils
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    James Cho A convenience utility class whose static methods provide a way to manipulate time information. Relies heavily on the format "hh:mm:ss:am".

      • compareTimes

        public static int compareTimes(java.lang.String mTime,
               java.lang.String anotherTime)
        Compares two times provided in "hh:mm:ss:am" format. Uses Comparable.compareTo(Object) logic.
        Parameters:
        mTime - A time in "hh:mm:ss:am" format.
        anotherTime - A time in "hh:mm:ss:am" format.
        Returns:
        int 0 if mTime and anotherTime are equal, 1 if mTime is more recent, -1 if anotherTime is more recent.

      • compareActivities

        public static int compareActivities(ActivityPojo current,
                    ActivityPojo another)
        Compares two provided ActivityPojo instances. Uses compareTimes(String, String). Useful for sorting. See ActivityPojo.compareTo(ActivityPojo).
        Parameters:
        current - An instance of ActivityPojo.
        another - Another instance of ActivityPojo.
        Returns:
        int 0 if current and another are equal, 1 if current is more recent, -1 if another is more recent.
        See Also:
        compareTimes(String, String), ActivityPojo.compareTo(ActivityPojo)
